378
00:23:59,478 --> 00:24:01,740
Did the boy ask her to be his girlfriend?

379
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:05,694
No. That didn't happen.

380
00:24:05,694 --> 00:24:07,987
Then, no.

381
00:24:07,987 --> 00:24:12,170
Unless they say "I like you" and ask each other out, it's just flirting.

382
00:24:12,931 --> 00:24:16,445
Do you have to say that kind of stuff?

383
00:24:16,445 --> 00:24:20,120
If you like each other, can't you just get each other with just a look?

384
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:23,583
There's a lot of kids out there who stop at that stage.

385
00:24:23,583 --> 00:24:25,715
Don't get yourself hurt

386
00:24:25,715 --> 00:24:29,428
and ask the boy out, get what you need, and be clear about it.

387
00:24:30,741 --> 00:24:34,032
But who is it? Who's the guy you're flirting with?

388
00:24:34,032 --> 00:24:37,726
Is it someone that I know too?

389
00:24:37,726 --> 00:24:40,519
No. It's nothing.

390
00:24:40,519 --> 00:24:42,152
This is suspicious.

391
00:24:42,152 --> 00:24:43,592
Ji Na, Sa Na.

392
00:24:43,592 --> 00:24:45,945
Go get the laundry from upstairs.

393
00:24:45,945 --> 00:24:47,946
Okay, Mom.

394
00:24:47,946 --> 00:24:49,428
Let's go.

395
00:25:07,446 --> 00:25:09,090
Seo Ro Bin.

396
00:25:09,747 --> 00:25:11,600
Stop acting out.

397
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:13,423
Stop acting like a child in front of Mom.

398
00:25:13,423 --> 00:25:15,264
What? Like a child?

399
00:25:15,264 --> 00:25:19,157
You're acting like a complete child now.

400
00:25:19,157 --> 00:25:21,931
You're whining that you don't want to go to the States.

401
00:25:21,931 --> 00:25:24,644
I could tell you were trying to tell her that you're having a hard time.

402
00:25:24,644 --> 00:25:26,675
What do you know?

403
00:25:26,675 --> 00:25:29,059
- Do you know how I feel?
- I don't.

404
00:25:29,059 --> 00:25:32,030
That's why I couldn't say anything until now.

405
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:34,564
But you've crossed the line.

406
00:25:34,564 --> 00:25:37,730
You need to grow up, Seo Ro Bin.

407
00:25:41,602 --> 00:25:44,073
So this is what you really think.

408
00:25:44,073 --> 00:25:45,565
Fine.

409
00:25:45,565 --> 00:25:49,247
Why don't you stop pretending to be the kind older brother?

410
00:25:49,247 --> 00:25:51,540
You're not my real brother.

411
00:25:53,073 --> 00:25:55,190
What did you just say?

412
00:25:56,124 --> 00:25:59,528
Wouldn't it be better for you if I wasn't around?

413
00:25:59,528 --> 00:26:01,722
Mom only needs you.

414
00:26:01,722 --> 00:26:04,594
What did you just say? You little...

415
00:26:18,017 --> 00:26:19,650
I'm sorry.

416
00:26:20,318 --> 00:26:21,892
