417
00:26:21,892 --> 00:26:23,282
Why?

418
00:26:23,923 --> 00:26:25,774
It's true.

419
00:26:25,774 --> 00:26:28,747
You and I, we're strangers.

420
00:26:28,747 --> 00:26:31,020
Seo Ro Bin, what's with you?

421
00:26:41,912 --> 00:26:44,160
Darn it.

422
00:26:48,068 --> 00:26:49,800
Ro Bin.

423
00:27:11,111 --> 00:27:13,932
I'm sorry, Oppa.

424
00:27:13,932 --> 00:27:16,700
I didn't mean to eavesdrop.

425
00:27:17,406 --> 00:27:20,840
It's okay. Why would you be sorry?

426
00:27:21,439 --> 00:27:23,270
But,

427
00:27:23,781 --> 00:27:26,215
is what Oppa Ro Bin said

428
00:27:26,215 --> 00:27:28,017
true?

429
00:27:33,162 --> 00:27:34,780
Yes.

430
00:27:35,243 --> 00:27:38,970
Ro Bin's real parents passed away when he was little.

431
00:27:39,418 --> 00:27:42,360
So my parents adopted him.

432
00:27:43,031 --> 00:27:47,176
Did you know from the very beginning?

433
00:27:47,176 --> 00:27:48,698
No.

434
00:27:50,150 --> 00:27:53,052
We didn't know until last year.

435
00:27:53,052 --> 00:27:55,310
We saw it by coincidence.

436
00:27:56,325 --> 00:27:59,120
But Ro Bin changed a lot after that.

437
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:05,540
He was a bright little rascal back then.

438
00:28:15,656 --> 00:28:17,460
