442
00:28:26,606 --> 00:28:27,828
I got you, didn't I?

443
00:28:27,828 --> 00:28:30,599
I ate the whole pizza by myself.

444
00:28:32,272 --> 00:28:33,483
Seo Ro Bin, you little...

445
00:28:33,483 --> 00:28:35,674
Come here. Get over here.

446
00:28:35,674 --> 00:28:37,076
- Why?
- What's with this?

447
00:28:37,076 --> 00:28:38,378
- What's wrong?
- You little...

448
00:28:38,378 --> 00:28:40,300
- Are you kidding me?
- What's wrong with it?

449
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:42,411
Get over here, you rascal.
